OL,3,CExtended Israel-Lebanon ceasefire 'not
OL,4,C100%', ambassador warns
OL,6,FAn extended ceasefire between Lebanon
OL,7,Fand Israel is "not 100%" and will need
OL,8,Fto be enforced, Israel's Ambassador to
OL,9,Fthe United Nations has said.
OL,11,FUS President Donald Trump announced on
OL,12,FThursday evening that a truce between
OL,13,Fthe two nations has been extended by
OL,14,Fthree weeks, following a second round
OL,15,Fof talks between officials in
OL,16,FWashington DC.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
