PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777161775
OL,3,CExtended Israel-Lebanon ceasefire 'not
OL,4,C100%', ambassador warns
OL,6,FTrump said the meeting between the
OL,7,FIsraeli and Lebanese ambassadors to
OL,8,Fthe US went "very well", but
OL,9,Facknowledged there was "Hezbollah to
OL,10,Fthink about", as the Iranian-backed
OL,11,Fmilitant group has opposed an
OL,12,Farmistice.
OL,14,FDanny Danon, Israel's Ambassador to
OL,15,Fthe UN, said the ceasefire was a
OL,16,F"significantly better situation" for
OL,17,Fboth countries but "not 100%".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
