OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777161775
OL,3,CExtended Israel-Lebanon ceasefire 'not
OL,4,C100%', ambassador warns
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"The Lebanese government have no
OL,12,Fcontrol of Hezbollah and Hezbollah is
OL,13,Fsending rockets trying to sabotage the
OL,14,Fceasefire. And Israel, we have to
OL,15,Fretaliate. Every time we see a threat,
OL,16,Fwe take action," Danon told ITV News'
OL,17,FNorth American partner CNN on Thursday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
