OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777161775
OL,3,CExtended Israel-Lebanon ceasefire 'not
OL,4,C100%', ambassador warns
OL,6,F"I hope ... to see that the Lebanese
OL,7,Fmilitary are actually able to
OL,8,Fimplement and to enforce this
OL,9,Fceasefire."
OL,11,FThe ceasefire initially came into
OL,12,Fforce on Friday last week, and there
OL,13,Fhave been multiple violations on both
OL,14,Fsides.
OL,16,FOn Thursday, Israel's military struck
OL,17,Fa missile launcher in Lebanon that had
OL,18,Ffired into the country in an attack
OL,19,Fclaimed by Hezbollah, who said it was
OL,20,Fretaliation for a strike on a Lebanese
OL,21,Fvillage that injured two people.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
