OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777161775
OL,3,CExtended Israel-Lebanon ceasefire 'not
OL,4,C100%', ambassador warns
OL,6,FLebanon's public health ministry also
OL,7,Fsaid an Israeli airstrike killed three
OL,8,Fpeople farther north of the country.
OL,9,FIsraeli military said the three were
OL,10,Fmilitants who had launched a missile
OL,11,Ftoward an Israeli warplane.
OL,13,FLebanon and Israel extend ceasefire
OL,15,FTrump confirmed on Thursday that
OL,16,FIsrael and Lebanon agreed to extend
OL,17,Ftheir ceasefire by three weeks
OL,18,Ffollowing talks at the White House.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
