PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777161775
OL,3,CExtended Israel-Lebanon ceasefire 'not
OL,4,C100%', ambassador warns
OL,6,FThe meeting "went very well," Trump
OL,7,Fsaid on his Truth Social platform,
OL,8,Fadding: "The United States is going to
OL,9,Fwork with Lebanon in order to help it
OL,10,Fprotect itself from Hezbollah."
OL,12,FSpeaking from the Oval Office, Israeli
OL,13,FAmbassador to the US Yechiel Leiter
OL,14,Fsaid the two natons had "never been
OL,15,Fnext to each other more than today".
OL,17,F"We are going to keep going, working
OL,18,Ffor peace. Let's hope we will get it
OL,19,Fas soon as possible," Leiter said.
