OL,3,CExtended Israel-Lebanon ceasefire 'not
OL,4,C100%', ambassador warns
OL,6,FLebanese Ambassador to the US Nada
OL,7,FHamadeh Moawad also thanked Trump for
OL,8,Fassisting in the "historic moment".
OL,10,F"I think with your help, with your
OL,11,Fsupport, we can make Lebanon great
OL,12,Fagain," Moawad said.
OL,14,FTrump 'won't rush' deal with Iran
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
