CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777161775
OL,3,CExtended Israel-Lebanon ceasefire 'not
OL,4,C100%', ambassador warns
OL,6,FThe US president said told reporters
OL,7,Fin the Oval Office "I don't want to
OL,8,Frush myself" as he pushed back against
OL,9,Fquestions that the conflict is
OL,10,Fexceeding the four-to-six week
OL,11,Ftimeline that he and aides previously
OL,12,Fset for the war.
OL,14,F"I took the country out militarily in
OL,15,Fthe first four weeks. I took it out
OL,16,Fmilitarily," Trump said.
OL,18,F"Now all we're doing is sitting back
OL,19,Fand seeing what deal (we make). And if
OL,20,Fthey don't want to make a deal, then
OL,21,FI'll finish it up militarily."
