OL,3,CExtended Israel-Lebanon ceasefire 'not
OL,4,C100%', ambassador warns
OL,6,FOn Thursday, Trump ordered the US
OL,7,Fmilitary to "shoot and kill" any
OL,8,FIranian small boats choking the Strait
OL,9,Fof Hormuz, which has been almost
OL,10,Fentirely closed since the war began.
OL,12,FThe US is intensifying its mine
OL,13,Fclearing efforts in the critical
OL,14,Fwaterway, the president said.
